Package: dcmtobids
Title: DICOM to BIDS Conversion with Dry-Run Planning
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Bradley R.",
           family = "Buchsbaum",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com")
Description: Provides an R implementation of DICOM sidecar matching and
    conversion to BIDS-style filenames and directories, with config
    validation, dry-run planning, and a command-line interface. This
    package is an independent R port that adapts behavior from the
    GPL-3-licensed dcm2bids Python project.
